\lim_{n\rightarrow \infty }\sum_{k=0}^{n} \frac{1}{{n \choose k}}
 \begin{align} \sum_{k=0}^n\frac1{\binom{n}{k}} &=2+\frac2n+\sum_{k=2}^{n-2}\frac1{\binom{n}{k}} \end{align} 
 \begin{align} \sum_{k=2}^{n-2}\frac1{\binom{n}{k}} &\le\frac{n-3}{\binom{n}{2}}\\ &=\frac{2(n-3)}{n(n-1)}\\[9pt] &\to0 \end{align} 
 \lim_{n\to\infty}\sum_{k=0}^n\frac1{\binom{n}{k}}=2 
n\geqslant4
